i got a digital camera for my birthday. that was sept. 4th. it took me a while to figure out all this crap on how to do it. it would of went much faster but i installed a program that overpowered everything else. what a downer that was. well now all is well. i went out on my boat on on birthdaywith ryan a sean. it was good. we all did something we were proud of. i finally drove the boat for my dad to water ski. ryan got up his first time (he hadn't done it in a while) and sean threw himself off the wake. seans a legend in that lake for his rope swingage that he almost died for. we all went to skaraua tokey. i have been going there for 6 years now on my birthday. love japanesse. then we all came back to my house for no reason but it was fun. ryan and my dad had a chess game with my nifty lord of the rings chess board. ohhh it was all out. RYAN WON that made him two and 0 in his chess career. he beet me and mt dad.but then i beet him the next day. my birthday was kind of a long time ago and nothing has been happening too much exept for school. we made TIGER BED HOBO t-shirts, we've now all worn them to school and we didnt get made fun of too much accually people were wanting to be in TBH. ha! screw them they dont know the first thing about hoboing.also at recess me sean jack and ryan take the whole 7th grade in a game. we kick the crap out of them! well yes everybody loves an update and esspecially one with pictures so here they are.

school is not that great being the "big wigs" as sean would say. i im not in anybodys class. the teachers are deffinatly harder. but besides for that it good. we rival crowningshield and pleasant street bus. i am currently looking into the black market to buy a rocket launcher to prove our superiority to our rive bus. i got one of the double lockers so its much bigger then everyone elses. me and sean are cracking down on the sogn making process  because we cant wait to make a home made demo. once they are made they will be given to people that would like one. soccer has started...but no! am i on anyones team...no! whatever i have learned to deal without friends. i've been practiceing my whole life. im looking forward to the end of school.

i had a good last day of summer yet it is still not over!!! it still hasnt hit me about getting back to school. it will i bet when i get on the bus. me and sean are going to bring caution tape to to keep the billion kindergardners back. today i went to get school supplies with my sister. then went to seans and made an aweosme movie about a taxi service (i have this awesome pimped out street bike that  fits 2 people on it. so that was the taxi. we all made millions. i went to my drum lesson. my teacher got pissed at me for the first tiem. it was scary because hes a huge guy that looks really tough. yet another week of d'yer mak'er. fun fun. i went back to seans and we did last day of summer stuff. me sean ryan and cait were outside and it started raining. amd we got all soaked. it was extreamly fun, except when when the rain got so hard it hurt. well school i hope goes good.

sleepover yesterday with sean eric and ryan, surprisingly we didn't beat the crap out of each other too much. but we went all out on some serious mini bike gaming. i spent most of today with taylin we first went to my house then then flos then her house and swam then the movies and saw without a paddle. it was very funny. taylin got a little into the tree falling on the people. taylin has a ghetto arm. a ghetto arm is when is moves a lot when flailed around without tensing. i do not have a ghetto arm.

hardcore hide and go seek yesterday with ryan and sean. that leaded up a new beat the crap out of eachother game. thats mosly what we do, beat the crap out of eachother. sean always randomly get a pIllow and starts beating ryan over the head. i then join in and ryan gets pissed. so they start throwwing the pIllow back a forth. it really pisses me of when they do that. i get really mad because we spend half our time doing that when we could be hoboing throwing around a pIllow. then thers sleeping bag wars which is the ultimate beat the crap out of each other game. it is basically everyone get into their sleeping bags and you go around jumping off of couches and stuff on to people. its not a true sleeping bag war if eric dosnt have a spaz though. he must have a spaz in order for it to be an official sleeping bag war. my tactic is useing unusual  slug like moves to attack and destroy. nothing to much going on . bye

today was suer cool. i went to amys for a get-together. it was very fun i must say. we al hoboed. (liz amy and two of the three Tiger Bed Hobos. did lots of other stuff but whatever. i havnt updated for awhile and as the saying goes everyone needs an update. yes they do fo sure. besides for going to amys i didnt do much. but i did have a good meatball sub. no really i woundl't announce what i had for dinner but this one was really out of the ordinary. me and sean played some ready to rumble to day and he usually always kicks my butt, but this time I k.oed him many times. i'd say we k.oed eachother about the same # of times. my aunt and ucle and my cousin austin left for long island in the morning today. ausin is way cool. i tought him how to hobo, and when someones does something good to go "props props props" while doing the hand flapping thing. it was pretty funny.

hey hobo zack here. hoboing is just soo great. my hobo group the TIGER BED HOBOS is the one and only hobo union. we've been hoboing a lot. its just so great....today i hung out with HOBO sean and HOBO ryan like always. i forgot what i did yesterday so screw yesterday. today we borrowed a bass from eric scalamo. its a fender!!! is so sweet. if only all seans equipment was working , ryan could play our songs with us. ehh. we went to the pizza place for some lunch. i had to write sean a contract saying i would pay him back. my cousin Austin is here, and my aunt and uncle are coming tonight so those are my plans for tonight. i also mowed the lawn today. wow it was so intense. hobo zack out, ehh thers nothing else to write.

TIGER BED HOBOS

Thankyou to all who took my survey, i know it was gay. the update on my life is.......yesterday i hung out with ryan sean and eric. we got some more signs. water supply ones. and that just goes along with seans upstairs garage whick is now awesome because me sean and ryan made it snazzin. yes it is cool beond imagination. the equipment is all at sean (in the upstairs garage) and we have been playing there the past two days. our forth song is in progress. so far we have a pre-choars and a choars. me jory and blaise had a huge rubber band fight today whick was pretty intense. i got nailed in the head a few times. then i went back to seans hung out with him and cait. we then got ready for the summerland fest. the time was winding down towards summerland and nobody had came to the fest yet. so we jumped around on the a mattress, while listening to caits new obsession. ryan and his sister showed up and that started that wild party. summerland was intense. i took lots of pictures so im sure cait will be posting them in her lj. im sure i forgot tons of stuff because everything is action packed...sort of:/

hey all, i got back from Canada at 2:30 in the morning last morning. it was ten hours. but i must say it wasnt bad i watch a very queer movie, and some black and wite war film. in canada...lets see, i met deanne fitspatrick. oh ya!!!!!!!!!! shes a rug hooker. sweet deal. i rowed an inflatable row boat to a sandbar. now that was a sweet deal. the cottage had a path to the beach to i went to the beach a lot. got my dairy queen and now im saving the cup. yup thats a tough one to explain. i did a lot of eating out. my mom is obsessive with her rug hooking so that just added to the slowness of my parents. yes its hard to remember all the stuff i did, but it was quite fun, and a nessesary retreat! but today i went to seans. just hung oaround with ryan and cait and sean. sweet deal. i having a very boring time now, all im doing is eating and drums. but thats all i ever do when im alone. ohhhh ya im pissed off do you know why person? i do and its because darkthrone made a whole new set up so now im back to level 1. wow THAT PISSES ME OF. im not liking the looks of my journal. so cait i know you will be reading this so help me make it better. you seem to have gotten quite good at overrides.

well today  was my last full day in the U.S for a week. im going to Canada. i dont really want to go. i guess it will be good. the car ride is 12 hours, plus my sister is taking her rode test before we go at like 6 a.m. that will add another hour!! but anyway, today i hung out with sean and ryan. didnt do much, but it was fun. we made another movie. it was awesome. it was about this rock star guy. but a blue screen would come up every time we tried to watch it at seans, so we watch it at ryans but the picture there was even weirder. then everything was just whatever. me and sean went back to my house, to drop me off. sean got his amp and guitar and left. he came back for his bike, he couldn't fit it so he left then he came back and rode my bike home. i mowed my lawn today, sean rode on the mower for a little while in circles. i got everything ready for darkthore, because im leaving so i put a lot into defense so i wouldn't get screwed while away for a week. but back to the car ride. 12 hours. wow. 12 hours wow. i can watch  movies on a lap top the whole time so. ya. ill listen to music. my cd's are offal though. who knows whats in Canada. i dont.  i have nothing to do. everything is so whatever. as sean would say my life is so whatever. when i come back i'd like if there were a lot of comments, at least ten ok? ya i want ten comments in this thing by the time im back. goodbye t oevryone, ill surely miss you all. remember 10, no less. canada has never met me before, i wonder if we will get along? bye.

today me and sean went up to coffe on the common with ryan, and we all got some good egg sandwitches. seans now collecting caps so we gave him our caps. those caps went through a lot. ryans fell over the counter, and then the lady tried to take them away (ryan saved them). after we went to seans house and made a movie about this fugitive guy from mexico. the tape ended right in the middle of filming.that was too bad because that movie we thought was accually going somewhere.we rode our bikes to my house and did stuff seans mom came and picked up sean and ryan just a few minutes ago. so now its very gloomy out and that is influencing my mood, which is gloomy. im going to Canada in two days. my thoughts on it change in a matter of 2 seconds. one minute i really do not want to go but then for about a second i want to, then its back to not wanting to go. the drive is 12 hours. its going to be longggggg. i've got some things i plan to do on the drive. but then once we get there is better be worth the drive. i mean it better be worth the drive!!! im not to sure whats going on tonight. im kind of tired. i thought maybe i was going to the movies, but ehhhh whatever.

sean is here for a few days. we have been practicing a lot to the 10th power. our 3rd song in now all instrumentally done, only two more verse lyrics still needed. yes not too much going on. tomarrow we hope to go to the club pool, and maybe hit up coffe on the common. sumerland was tonight. great as usual. i dislike poop in the pants very much. we need a name really bad!!! but there are absolutly no ideas for one (last time sean put an entry in his journal about a name he got 22 comments, i would like to have that also) things are just better when people comment.

Who likes the fist. i do. and you do care. well band practice today. our 3rd song is pretty much done. just need to write some more lyrics and practice to make it flaless. after that sean went home. then he came back. and amy came over. we didnt do much. but it was all and all a good time. so i have been obsessing over a game called dark throne. oh ya i am stealthxfire. so fear me. if i tell you to click on a link or its in my away message click it because im just recruiting you to get more citizens. i think peopel are getting pissed at me though, because i send the link to people constantly. they ask what it is...and i dont reply. then the next day i tell them to click it. again. seans been leaving his guitar here and the only thing im good at is power choard. so  thats always fun. i've got my drum lessontomarrow and im sick of the song hes teaching me called "d'yer mak'er" is a led zeppline so so thats good to know. if you don't comment dont think your so sly because i know who reads this and i will be furious at you! syonara

after mathas vineyard with sean, things around here got pretty dull. but anyways yesterday was band pratice. right now our 3rd song is in its creation. we played outside because it was nice out. once we think of a name that we plan to keep, we will make a band livejournal serving as a website. but today was a dull as light bulb. but i did set up for this game i joined called "dark throne" its very cool. my mom came home from her work thing today that she had been at all week, so we might go out to dinner tonight, but i dont think that will happen. there is really nothing going on these days. kind of depressing. eh?

after mathas vineyard with sean, things around here got pretty dull. but anyways yesterday was band pratice. right now our 3rd song is in its creation. we played outside because it was nice out. once we think of a name that we plan to keep, we will make a band livejournal serving as a website. but today was a dull as light bulb. but i did set up for this game i joined called "dark throne" its very cool. my mom came home from her work thing today that she had been at all week, so we might go out to dinner tonight, but i dont think that will happen. there is really nothing going on these days. kind of depressing. eh?

yo yo yo i felt the need to update because i havn't for a long time, and i suppose that people are probably getting bored with my temp. so i'm just updating even though i have my stupid drums going through everything. if you know how to put them in back of my entries i would greatly appriciate it if you would tell me because zack ferguson and overrides are enemies. me sean and his mom got back from marthats vineyard tonight. it feels good to be home even though its really cool there, seans peoples house is intensly hardcore. we mostly hung out with kim and cait while they babysat (making it easier for them) but its a very deselate place out there so theres not much to do. we went to the beach a lot which is about two feet away, and one time i was walking on this cool thing in a cliff and i hit my toe on a random rock. i was like "sean you have no idea how bad this hurts" then i look at my toe and its all bloody and the nail is about to fall off. we walked a litte bit and sean ran ahead to go get someone. i was left limping down the beach for quite some time. but then we got back and cleaned it up. there was also some hardcore sand city building going on. NOW COMMENT
I am in the process of making my livejournal unbelievebly cool. Regular updates will be posted on Stick Your Face in the Candles as soon as I am done.

thank you to everyone who commented in my last entry, i greatly appriciate it. and a spacial thanks to cait who did my icon. like i told you last time on Stick Your Face in the Candles my life was getting pretty dull. but since then its got way better. i've hung out with the same people but we've been doing more exilerating forms of entertainment. yesterday i hung out with sean and ryan and eric. we got another cone. (the new cone is seans icon)i'm having trouble remembering what i did yesterday but I had a good time. ohhh ya we made a movie . it was good this movie was a long term idea of my. heres the plot. these kids are like"i've never seen my self sleep before so lets tape ourselfs sleeping" so they do it and the next day they watch it and they see a guy come in their house and never leave. so then we watched "you got served" oh my! that was a terrible terrible movie. for the love of anyone it was so bad sean turned his back to it because he didnt think it deserved his support by watching it. eric and sean both fell asleep during it. the we did some hardcore sleepage, and had cinimon buns in the morning. they were really good. soon after we played a neighborhood wide capture the flag. no one won because it just randomly ended because eric had a spaz because i got him in jail. then we didnt not anything much for a while and eric had another spaz at the fact of that. that was his third spaz becasue the night becase he went midevil on ryan because ryan hit him in the eye with a pillow. eric went home and then we made ryan a journal. (his icon should be mine because its practically all my stuff) but its call "r_u_yoing_me" that phrase comes from another movie when ryan was a ghettoer and he said "r u yoing me?". but then ryan went home. so me and sean and his sister went outside. sean rode circles around us while we sat on their car. so after that long term sitting session the pizza guy cam and i gave him the money. i was really good at it. we ate the papa ginos pizza and me and sean went to my house where we palyed the mini bike game and ate ice creme. syonara.

today like all days i hung out with sean. eric came over, we did stuff and made a movie. it was about street hocky. it was very weird. he left. we still hung out. i hade my drums over there so we played. i'm very excited because my drum teacher gave me cool new things to practice, and next week i get to learn some tunes! oh ya i cant wait. i dont like the weather these days. i havnt gotten to go wakeboarding once!!! i havn't even gone swimming all summer. bummer:/

yes so this update in my journal is mainly for apperance. i've noticed how unattractive my journal is becoming. i like the black and white apperance, but maybe it's the layout. i'm no "livejournal lord" so its going to have to stay this way for now. i also hate the fact that i have all my entries showing, it would be so hardcore if only the latest one showed, and then you could click on something to view my past entries. maybe i will spend a day trying to figure out all the tricks of livejournals, that way i would know all the tricks of livejournals....new subject...well me and sean have had practice just about everyday this week and it has payed off. we have all of our parts to "quell down" no word but its still sounds good. and now that "motivates you" is finished for quite some time now, sean  is able to multitask to it now. yes sean can sing and play because the song is now second nature to him.. i hope this make my journal b.e.a.u.tiful. syonara.

Hey all. how do you like those wonderful pictures that cait took? notice we were outside? yeah we joke about calling ourselfs " we move a lot" because we play where ever we feel like. outside, inside, seans house, my house. ya so our goal is to play at the summer jam next year.some members would be nice! seriously no body plays anything. its very bothersome oh ya that reminds me of something. the summer jam this year. i can describe it to you in one word. that depressing word is rain. yup everyone was there some rain started, they said we'll wait it out. some thunder and lightning started and they packed up. so annoying, really i love the summer jam. so i just had my dad pick me up at the pizza place. I am outraged at the fact of this! syanara
got a new song we are working on "quell down" and just finished the last one "motivates you". thank you catie for taking the time to mess up my journal.
check out these pictures yo

Journal update...yesterday was fun. In the morning i did absolutely nothing! but then it got better. i went to the battle of the bands in sterling with sean where we met amy there. there was lots of great bands. I believe Beware of the dog came in first, Double helix came in second, and from this farewell came in third. my personal favorite band was From this farewell. some kid got arrestest. it brought much exitment to me at that moment. when beware of the dog finished their set the drummer threw his sticks into the crowd. i got one, although i did have to beg some girl for it. Over all it was a good show. today i went golfing with mike and jory. he brought his new camcorder, and we taped lots of stuff. then i came home, and a a big fathers day bash. e got my dad a hamock. school tomarrow and its the last day! alright syanora.

School is almost out!!!!! theres 4 more days. i can not wait. summer is gong to be so kick butt! summer jam is going to be the jam with amy dand. our master plan has been aborted amy! too bad. its very annoying how there is 4 more days of school left and the teachers still have tests scheduled, and they are not letting up on the work either! i know high school kids have finals and all, but it would be nice to have it easy for the last couple of days. I dont really have many summer plans. pretty dpressing. but i do believe i may go to marthas vineyard with sean, and then we are going surfing in rhode islande. hey maybe i do have summer plans! last year me and sean went to new port to surf for one day. this year i think our sisters are coming and we arwe staying over night. Any way, today was a very boring day at school. i made a way cool mushroom stamp in art! i also made a lotto smash one. the shroom came out way better. i'm abandoned tonight. we have no food!!! i'v been home alone since 3:00. iv been bored out  of my mind. and that is the conclusion of my saga.

Yesterday was thursday. it was pretty jamming. We went to the zoo! ya it was a zoo not to exiting. but i did get a lolly pop and a way cool pencil. only cost me $1.68. the lady at the cash register was so into her job. i spent $1.68 cents and she said "thatnk you oh so very much for purchasing these items, and have a wonderful day here at Roger Williams Park Zoo. Kind of queer, but she was an old gramma so that made all the more cool.then mrs. calio yelled at me because she couldnt  find me. the bus ride home was ok. i zoned out just listening to music, mostly a static lullaby.
